reviewText: I am happy to have received this to add to my collection of Bai Ling movies.
bought it for the character portrails - very good!
I only bought it because Dana Delany is in it but you hardly see her. Very disappointing.
I met bai ling 2 times. she is a great actress ,nice person and a beautiful woman.she has done  a lot of great work and does not get her due.
